summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the West Seattle Freeway Project, authorizing construction of the Harbor Island Approach Structure (Contract 5) from approximately Klickitat Avenue Southwest to approximately 300 feet east of the Duwamish East Waterway, authorizing the hiring of consultants and the awarding of contracts, increasing expenditure allowances in the 1980 Budget of the Engineering Department, and making an appropriation from the Engineering Operating Fund reimbursable from the West Seattle Freeway Fund.
